metadata.name: Hunters Eye
metadata.description:
By the light of a moon so old, this world glows.   This is the evening when success is measured in will of intent and blending in with the surroundings.  A babbling brooke masks ones approach and lulls the minds of the prey into a false sense of security.  A crisp,  bustling,  gale masks the scent of all and cleanses the landscape.  Your time is now... 

All is on display this evening and the heavens watch.
